This respitory cosntains the code developed to run benchmarks from CloudSuite and Hadoop. It has four benchmark control modules for Hadoop, Web Search, Web Service and Graph Analysis.

The benchmark control modules are in the directory "powertrade".

The common modules contains the java modules for controlling XenServer installed on the testbed machines, a metering module to log power reading from APC power strip that powers the testbed servers, a second power module to log power using WattsUp power meters thorugh serial port, and SSH module to send commands and recieve response from the servers and power devices.
